	<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3 style="padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.222em; font-size: 1.286em;"><span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;"><span style="font-size: 14;"><span style="font-size: 18;">It is Here!  Merb Course on RubyLearning.Org</span><br /></span></span></h3><h3 style="padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.222em; font-size: 1.286em;"><span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;"><span style="font-size: 14;">As mentioned in a prior post, the Merb Course has been a success.  The official beginning of registration has opened up today, and the course starts on 10th Jan. 2009. You first need to <a href="http://rubylearning.org/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(35, 97, 161); text-decoration: underline;">register on the site</a>and then <a href="http://rubylearning.org/class/course/view.php?id=19" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(35, 97, 161); text-decoration: underline;">enroll into the course</a>. On registration, you can download the “Introduction to Merb” eBook.</span><br /></span></h3><h3 style="padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.222em; font-size: 1.286em;"><span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;"><span style="line-height: 18px; font-size: 12;"></span></span></h3><h3 style="padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.222em; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.286em;">
<span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;">Early Bird Registration Discounts</span> <span style="font-size: small;"> </span>
</h3><ol>
<li><span style="font-size: small;">For the first 25 registrations, Course Fee: US$ 6 per participant</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: small;">After the first 25 registrations, Course Fee US$ 8 per participant till 31st Dec. 2008</span></li>
<li>
<span style="font-size: small;"> </span><span style="font-size: small;">From 1st Jan. 2009, Course Fee US$ 10 per participant</span>
</li>
</ol><br /><div style="padding: 0px;"><span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;">The course fee goes towards maintaining RubyLearning and helps provide quality content to you.</span></div><div style="padding: 0px;"><span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;">So hurry, registrations have started. </span></div><div style="padding: 0px;"><span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;">See full details at <a href="http://rubylearning.com/blog/2008/12/06/introduction-to-merb-a-new-course/">rubylearning.com/blog</a></span></div><span style="line-height: 22px; font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 14;"></span><div class="blogger-post-footer"><img class="posterous_download_image" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/2949792777916502048-4619231994624248688?l=vgoff.blogspot.com" height="1" alt="" width="1" /></div>]]></content:encoded>
